data.description: Are you looking for a cozy home in Boise with a great location and plenty of space? Then check out this charming property across from Capital High School. This house has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a family room, a living room, and an updated kitchen. You'll love the hardwood floors throughout the house, giving it an open and elegant feel. The only thing this house needs is a fresh coat of paint, which you can choose to match your personal style. AND, brand new AC unit and thermostat, that's huge! Don't miss this opportunity to own a lovely home in a convenient and desirable neighborhood with noooo HOA's!
